# +---------------------------------+
# |   RISCV K1 Cache Configuration  |
# +---------------------------------+
# Note: L1 sets 128 and L2 sets 512. 
# but, we obtain a best performance with 512 sets for L1 and 1024 for L2.
# https://gitee.com/bianbu-linux/linux-6.1/blob/bl-v1.0.y/arch/riscv/boot/dts/spacemit/k1-x.dtsi
# https://lore.kernel.org/all/20240703-k1-01-basic-dt-v3-8-12f73b47461e@gentoo.org/
#Level	SL	NL	CL	WL
1	32768	512	64	4
2	524288	1024	64	16
3	4194304	4096	64	16
